\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y'=1y'+xy''+f'\left(y'\right)y''
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
y''\left(x+f'\left(y'\right)\right)=0
\]

\end_inset

שני מקרים:
\end_layout

